OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers this evening, frequent and
OL,7,Fprolonged in places, with a chance of
OL,8,Fhail and thunder. Further showers
OL,9,Fovernight mixed with clear spells,
OL,10,Fbefore turning more generally wet
OL,11,Flater. Breezy at times and staying
OL,12,Frather windy in coastal regions. Mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FFrequent showers merging
OL,15,Finto more general rain at times, with
OL,16,Fa chance of thunder. Turning
OL,17,Fincreasingly windy and feeling cool,
OL,18,Fbut warmer in any sunshine and out of
OL,19,Fthe wind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
