OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMuch
OL,6,Fdrier on Friday with sunny intervals,
OL,7,Fbut a few showers are possible.
OL,8,FUnseasonably windy for some at first
OL,9,Fon Saturday with further rain at times
OL,10,Fover the weekend.
